item.title: Free Domain
item.dc:creator: @Mopman Mopman
item.description:
@Mopman wrote:

awesom:

rofl… Dude you seriously can’t speak for everyone so don’t talk shit…I know a lot of free domain forums with a lot of active members…Maybe you don’t take them seriously but TBH if the only reason you don’t is cuz it’s a free domain then your over geeky and should get out more…No one should care whether it’s free or not it should only matter what its about and the content in it and how useful it can be…What you can learn and do on a forum is what makes it good not the fact that someone paid to get.com on the end or not seriously…

Actually, starting a successful website takes capital 99.9% of the time. If someone had to go with a free domain rather than paying the whole couple of dollars for a real one, they didn’t have any capital and the website is doomed to fail.
